Season 1, Episode 04 - Travis & Davey
 Travis, a 36-year-old virgin, turns to online dating to find his bride. This devout Christian has high expectations. His future wife must be beautiful, virtuous, love the Lord and appreciate his desire to remain a virgin until marriage.
